data.title: Closed for good at this location
data.text: We came to Beijing Wok to pick up some Chinese food for dinner.  We found that the Beijing Wok has closed and that the location is now an Indian and Pakistani restaurant  The website is no longer functional.

data.title: Good value
data.text: Good location, though very limited parking. This is a small corner storefront on a busy street. Far enough from the shopping center that it wasn't busy at noon the day after Christmas. Portions were large, everyone enjoyed what they had - the lunch specials are a great value.
